des:
Ask Alexa to open Gem Reading
Alexa will welcome you and select the best gem for you
She will provide how to use the gem, its energy, and guidance.
Ask Alexa daily for a gem reading or more often if you are so inclined. 
Charmed in Company LLP is the oldest Mystical Metaphysical shoppe in NJ. We created this skill to give insight into some of the properties and uses of gemstones. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
